0.name: VERTICAL SPACE INTERIORS, INC.
0.address: ADDRESS: Unit B & C IPMC Building No. 268, Barangay Niog 3 Bacoor, Cavite, 4102 Philippines
desc: OVERVIEW: Vertical Space Interiors, Inc. was established in Dubai, United Arab Emirates on February 2007. Since then, it has successfully completed numerous projects in the Gulf region as well as in India and Africa. The Company has carved out its niche in the retail interiors market – delivering turn-key jobs and manufacturing custom-built furniture for some of the most prominent brands today.

The Company operates a 1000-square meter carpentry workshop, with an adjoining 500-square meter painting area – both fully equipped with the latest tools and machines vital to the services we provide. The factory is located in the heart of the Al Quoz Industrial Area in Dubai, UAE.

More than the latest machines and equipment, more than high-grade materials, the caliber of our work is driven by people behind it. Each piece of furniture that comes out our workshop is made from raw skill and talent. Each project we hand over is built on unrelenting work ethic and commitment to quality.

The diversity of our talents is reflected in the projects we have completed. We employ experience project managers, interior designers, architects, engineers and skilled workers who are engaged in sustained efforts to deliver the best results to our valued clients.

Building on the success of the operation in Dubai, the Company has since opened its offices in Abu Dhabi, UAE and in the Philippines – catering to its Sales & Marketing Unit and Design Services Units, respectively.

2.name: GRAIA CONSTRUCTION CORPORATION
2.address: ADDRESS: KM 18 Aguinaldo Highway Bacoor, Cavite, 4102 Philippines
desc: OVERVIEW: GRAIA Construction Corporation started out in 2003 as a supply company servicing Metro Manila, Bataan, Cavite and Palawan.

With the company’s vision constantly at the forefront of its operations, GRAIA’s namesake has become synonymous with construction excellence having widened its portfolio of projects for over a decade. GRAIA’s unchanging commitment to “client-first” service has earned the trust of discerning clients throughout the years.

Within three years, the company was able to expand its services and venture into the construction industry, paving the way to become one of the most reputable construction companies in the business. Slowly, the company was able to acquire the necessary equipment and machinery to support larger-scale operations. Since then, the GRAIA brand of service was able to reach farther provincial areas across the Philippines.

Currently, though proven an indomitable force in the construction industry, GRAIA still strives to further expand its services to keep up with client demands, ensuring quality workmanship, punctuality, and professionalism.
